reviewText: It's great to see films that are inspiring and not just about sex, drugs and violence. Kibwe brings a timeless message to never give up and it's a message that should never grow old! Kibwe is a hidden gem, I pray Tyler Perry or David Talbert get a chance to see his work and feature him in one of their plays or movies his voice is truly unique and worthy to share with the world. I am anxious to see more from him and to see how he grows and improves on each project. I am inspired.
